{"tid":1684982,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[禁制令］申請禁制令真係咁容易？","createTime":"2019-10-31T10:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T11:03:30.000Z","uid":325081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e61cd3a0082fde1a41c6edb911ba9fe110c7cae1","tid":1684982,"uid":325081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:50:40.000Z","msg":"嗱，之前用左緊急法呢，就俾人批評到體無全膚。<br />\n<br />\n咁而家呢，我就唔用緊急法喇，不過呢就照「立法」禁制你。<br />\n<br />\n禁止你言論自由；禁止你去行街去機場；禁止你披露犯法警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />資料等你地告都無得告。<br />\n<br />\n咁呢，下次可以禁止埋你唔解鎖電話；禁止埋你電話用screen lock password，禁止埋你兩隻腳行路；禁止埋你唔同警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />敬禮⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n其實，有無人可以去申請禁制令，禁止警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />使用警棍；禁止警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />使用任何槍械；禁止警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />蒙面等等？<br />\n<br />\n點解人地可以申請，我地無人去搞？"},{"pid":"fd1f28bff2816038f084f1226d1bc30c3f2fb998","tid":1684982,"uid":35155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T10:53:47.000Z","msg":"禁止政府胡亂申請禁制令"},{"pid":"76a20516c9571e1a761839f2d9c577b50a4522c3","tid":1684982,"uid":325081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:03:11.000Z","msg":"所有屋苑，去申請禁制令，禁止警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在沒有搜查令之下入屋苑執法"},{"pid":"4f423b0ab35d3b359a0454b50542a0c3637bd68a","tid":1684982,"uid":319181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T11:03:30.000Z","msg":"我諗，香港好多人都想同大灣區全面接軌&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1684606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1684606</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}